<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Selfish"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Justin Timberlake"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Everything I Thought It Was"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="USRC12400001"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1727024908"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2134655386"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2134697590"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="5GSYbwIInbmPvNRyl7nDpR"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="000ny9FY4fQ5x1"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="00253Lzb39p8o5"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="476318718"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="476612251"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:47.150"><div begin="9.990" end="3:47.150"><p begin="9.990" end="10.170" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="9.990" end="10.170">Uh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">嗯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">嗯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ああ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ay</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">É</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ох</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah</span></p><p begin="11.690" end="14.060" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="11.690" end="11.860">If</span> <span begin="11.860" end="12.020">they</span> <span begin="12.020" end="12.240">saw</span> <span begin="12.240" end="12.410">wha</span><span begin="12.410" end="12.450">t</span> <span begin="12.450" end="12.920">I</span> <span begin="13.020" end="14.060">saw</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">倘若他们能看见我眼中的风景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">倘若他們能看見我眼中的風景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">僕が見たものを彼らが見たなら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 본 걸 그들도 보았다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S&apos;ils voyaient ce que j&apos;ai vu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si vieran lo que yo vi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn sie sähen was ich sah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se eles vissem o que eu vi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если бы они видели то что видел я</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se vedessero quello che ho visto io</span></p><p begin="14.780" end="16.940" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="14.780" end="14.930">They</span> <span begin="14.930" end="15.090">would</span> <span begin="15.090" end="15.460">fall</span> <span begin="15.460" end="15.830">the</span> <span begin="15.830" end="16.170">way</span> <span begin="16.170" end="16.300">I</span> <span begin="16.430" end="16.940">fell</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">他们定会像我这般无可救药地沦陷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">他們定會像我這般無可救藥地淪陷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">僕のように恋に落ちるだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나처럼 너에게 빠졌을 텐데</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ils tomberaient comme je suis tombé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se enamorarían como yo me enamoré</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Würden sie sich verlieben wie ich mich verliebte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eles se apaixonariam do jeito que me apaixonei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Они бы влюбились так же как влюбился я</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perderebbero la testa come l&apos;ho persa io</span></p><p begin="16.980" end="19.390" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="16.980" end="17.050">But</span> <span begin="17.160" end="17.320">they</span> <span begin="17.320" end="17.510">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="17.510" end="17.660">know</span> <span begin="17.660" end="17.850">what</span> <span begin="17.850" end="18.500">you</span> <span begin="18.500" end="19.330">wan</span><span begin="19.330" end="19.390">t</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但他们不懂你心底的渴望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">但他們不懂你心底的渴望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">でも君が何を望んでいるか 彼らは知らない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하지만 그들은 네가 뭘 원하는지 몰라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mais ils ne savent pas ce que tu veux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pero ellos no saben lo que tú quieres</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aber sie wissen nicht was du willst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mas eles não sabem o que você quer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но они не знают чего ты хочешь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ma loro non sanno cosa desideri</span></p><p begin="20.050" end="22.480" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="20.050" end="20.220">And,</span> <span begin="20.220" end="20.400">ba</span><span begin="20.400" end="20.600">by,</span> <span begin="20.600" end="20.920">I</span> <span begin="20.920" end="21.100">woul</span><span begin="21.100" end="21.260">d</span> <span begin="21.260" end="21.600">ne</span><span begin="21.600" end="21.940">ver</span> <span begin="21.940" end="22.480">tell</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">而宝贝 我也绝不会向外人言说</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">而寶貝 我也絕不會向外人言說</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そしてベイビー 僕が教えることは絶対にない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그리고, 베이비, 난 절대 말해주지 않을 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et bébé je ne le dirais jamais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y, nena, yo nunca se los diría</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und Schatz ich würde es niemals verraten</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E, baby, eu nunca contaria</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И малышка я им ни за что не расскажу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E, piccola, io non lo direi mai</span></p><p begin="22.620" end="24.900" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="22.620" end="22.690">I</span><span begin="22.690" end="22.780">f</span> <span begin="22.780" end="22.970">they</span> <span begin="22.970" end="23.120">knew</span> <span begin="23.120" end="23.310">wha</span><span begin="23.310" end="23.340">t</span> <span begin="23.340" end="24.010">I</span> <span begin="24.010" end="24.900">know</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">倘若他们知晓我拥有的秘密</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">倘若他們知曉我擁有的秘密</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">僕が知っていることを彼らが知ったなら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 아는 걸 그들도 알았다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S&apos;ils savaient ce que je sais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si supieran lo que yo sé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn sie wüssten was ich weiß</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se eles soubessem o que eu sei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если бы они знали то что знаю я</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se sapessero quello che so</span></p><p begin="25.670" end="27.990" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.670" end="25.860">They</span> <span begin="25.860" end="25.940">would</span> <span begin="26.060" end="26.370">ne</span><span begin="26.370" end="26.750">ver</span> <span begin="26.750" end="27.070">let</span> <span begin="27.070" end="27.400">you</span> <span begin="27.400" end="27.990">go</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">他们绝对舍不得放开你的手</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">他們絕對捨不得放開你的手</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">決して君を手放さないだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">절대 널 놓아주지 않았을 텐데</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ils ne te laisseraient jamais partir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nunca te dejarían ir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Würden sie dich niemals gehen lassen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eles nunca te deixariam ir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Они бы никогда тебя не отпустили</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non ti lascerebbero mai andare</span></p><p begin="28.230" end="29.410" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="28.230" end="28.410">So</span> <span begin="28.410" end="28.660">gue</span><span begin="28.660" end="28.790">ss</span> <span begin="28.790" end="29.410">what?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">所以你知道吗？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">所以你知道嗎？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だからどうだか分かるかい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래서 그거 알아?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors devine quoi ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Así que ¿adivina qué?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Also weißt du was</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Então adivinha?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Так что знаешь что</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quindi indovina un po&apos;?</span></p><p begin="29.770" end="32.060" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.770" end="29.940">I</span> <span begin="29.940" end="30.130">ain&apos;t</span> <span begin="30.130" end="30.480">ne</span><span begin="30.480" end="30.830">ver</span> <span begin="30.830" end="31.020">let</span><span begin="31.020" end="31.170">ting</span> <span begin="31.170" end="31.380">you</span> <span begin="31.480" end="32.060">go</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我生生世世都不会放你离开</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我生生世世都不會放你離開</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">僕は絶対に君を手放さない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">난 절대 널 놓지 않을 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne te laisserai jamais partir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo nunca te dejaré ir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich werde dich niemals gehen lassen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu nunca vou te deixar ir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я тебя никогда не отпущу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io non ti lascerò mai andare</span></p><p begin="32.130" end="35.060" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.130" end="32.800">&apos;Cau</span><span begin="32.800" end="32.860">se</span> <span begin="32.860" end="33.390">your</span> <span begin="33.390" end="33.540">li</span><span begin="33.540" end="33.740">ps</span> <span begin="33.740" end="33.920">were</span> <span begin="34.050" end="34.330">made</span> <span begin="34.330" end="34.440">for</span> <span begin="34.560" end="35.060">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只因你的双唇天生就该被我亲吻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只因你的雙唇天生就該被我親吻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君の唇は僕のものになるために作られたから</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 입술은 내 입술을 위해 만들어졌으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Car tes lèvres ont été faites pour les miennes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque tus labios fueron hechos para los míos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Denn deine Lippen sind für meine gemacht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque os seus lábios foram feitos para os meus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведь твои губы созданы для моих</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché le tue labbra sono state fatte per le mie</span></p><p begin="35.400" end="37.710" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="35.400" end="35.580">And</span> <span begin="35.580" end="36.060">my</span> <span begin="36.060" end="36.270">heart</span> <span begin="36.400" end="36.470">would</span> <span begin="36.590" end="36.750">go</span> <span begin="36.850" end="36.950">f</span><span begin="36.950" end="37.280">lat</span><span begin="37.280" end="37.710">line</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我的心跳大概会骤然停息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我的心跳大概會驟然停息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そして僕の心臓は止まってしまうだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 심장은 멈춰버리고 말 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et mon cœur s&apos;arrêterait de battre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y mi corazón se detendría</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und mein Herz würde aufhören zu schlagen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E o meu coração iria parar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А моё сердце бы просто остановилось</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E il mio battito si azzererebbe</span></p><p begin="38.110" end="41.990" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.110" end="38.200">I</span><span begin="38.200" end="38.300">f</span> <span begin="38.300" end="38.680">i</span><span begin="38.680" end="38.750">t</span> <span begin="38.750" end="39.020">wa</span><span begin="39.020" end="39.150">s</span><span begin="39.150" end="39.340">n&apos;t</span> <span begin="39.480" end="39.840">bea</span><span begin="39.840" end="39.980">ting</span> <span begin="39.980" end="40.380">for</span> <span begin="40.380" end="40.570">you</span> <span begin="40.680" end="41.020">all</span> <span begin="41.020" end="41.070">the</span> <span begin="41.190" end="41.990">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">倘若它不是每时每刻都在为你跳动</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">倘若它不是每時每刻都在為你跳動</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">いつも君のために脈打っていなければ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">항상 널 위해 뛰고 있는 게 아니라면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S&apos;il ne battait pas pour toi tout le temps</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si no estuviera latiendo por ti todo el tiempo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn es nicht die ganze Zeit nur für dich schlagen würde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se não estivesse batendo por você o tempo todo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если бы оно не билось всё время ради тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se non battesse per te tutto il tempo</span></p><p begin="42.480" end="46.990" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.480" end="42.740">So</span> <span begin="42.740" end="42.830">i</span><span begin="42.830" end="42.910">f</span> <span begin="42.910" end="43.260">I</span> <span begin="43.260" end="43.630">get</span> <span begin="43.730" end="44.130">jea</span><span begin="44.130" end="44.250">lou</span><span begin="44.250" end="44.420">s,</span> <span begin="45.630" end="45.950">I</span> <span begin="45.950" end="46.410">can</span><span begin="46.410" end="46.480">&apos;t</span> <span begin="46.480" end="46.840">hel</span><span begin="46.840" end="46.880">p</span> <span begin="46.880" end="46.990">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">所以若我吃醋嫉妒 那也是情难自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">所以若我吃醋嫉妒 那也是情難自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だから嫉妬しても 仕方がないんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그러니 내가 질투하더라도, 어쩔 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors si je suis jaloux je n&apos;y peux rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Así que si me pongo celoso, no puedo evitarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn ich also eifersüchtig werde kann ich nichts dafür</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Então se eu fico com ciúmes, não consigo evitar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поэтому если я ревную ничего не могу с собой поделать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quindi se divento geloso, non ci posso fare niente</span></p><p begin="48.350" end="52.610" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.350" end="48.720">I</span> <span begin="48.720" end="49.220">wan</span><span begin="49.220" end="49.250">t</span> <span begin="49.250" end="49.570">eve</span><span begin="49.570" end="49.620">ry</span> <span begin="49.730" end="50.040">bi</span><span begin="50.040" end="50.090">t</span> <span begin="50.090" end="50.230">of</span> <span begin="50.230" end="50.880">you,</span> <span begin="50.880" end="50.970">I</span> <span begin="51.080" end="51.260">gue</span><span begin="51.260" end="51.430">ss</span> <span begin="51.430" end="51.860">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="51.860" end="52.250">sel</span><span begin="52.250" end="52.490">fi</span><span begin="52.490" end="52.610">sh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我想要霸占你的每一分每一寸 我想我就是这般自私</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我想要霸佔你的每一分每一寸 我想我就是這般自私</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君の全てが欲しい 僕は自分勝手なんだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너의 모든 것을 원해, 내가 이기적인가 봐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux chaque parcelle de toi je suppose que je suis égoïste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero cada parte de ti, supongo que soy egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich will jedes Stückchen von