egin="1:23.180" end="1:23.340">you</span> <span begin="1:23.340" end="1:23.750">e</span><span begin="1:23.750" end="1:23.800">ve</span><span begin="1:23.800" end="1:23.930">ry</span><span begin="1:23.930" end="1:24.640">thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我想把一切全都倾诉于你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我想把一切全都傾訴於你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君に全てを伝えたい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너에게 모든 걸 말해주고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux tout te dire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero decirte todo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich möchte dir alles sagen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu quero te contar tudo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу рассказать тебе всё</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio raccontarti tutto</span></p><p begin="1:25.680" end="1:27.730" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:25.680" end="1:25.820">E</span><span begin="1:25.820" end="1:25.850">ve</span><span begin="1:25.850" end="1:26.000">ry</span><span begin="1:26.000" end="1:26.370">thing</span> <span begin="1:26.370" end="1:26.640">tha</span><span begin="1:26.640" end="1:26.760">t&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:26.760" end="1:27.060">on</span> <span begin="1:27.060" end="1:27.390">my</span> <span begin="1:27.390" end="1:27.730">mind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">把我脑海中翻涌的思绪全都告诉你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">把我腦海中翻湧的思緒全都告訴你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">僕の心にある全てのことを</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 마음속에 있는 모든 것을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tout ce que j&apos;ai en tête</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Todo lo que está en mi mente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Alles was mir auf dem Herzen liegt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tudo o que está na minha mente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Всё что у меня на уме</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tutto ciò che ho nella testa</span></p><p begin="1:27.730" end="1:30.190" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:27.730" end="1:27.880">An</span><span begin="1:27.880" end="1:27.910">d</span> <span begin="1:27.910" end="1:28.070">I</span> <span begin="1:28.070" end="1:28.270">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:28.270" end="1:28.400">want</span> <span begin="1:28.400" end="1:28.570">a</span><span begin="1:28.570" end="1:28.780">ny</span> <span begin="1:28.780" end="1:29.260">o</span><span begin="1:29.260" end="1:29.430">ther</span> <span begin="1:29.430" end="1:30.080">guy</span><span begin="1:30.080" end="1:30.190">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我可不希望有任何其他男人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我可不希望有任何其他男人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">他の男たちには</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그리고 다른 어떤 남자들도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et je ne veux aucun autre garçon</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y no quiero a ningún otro chico</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und ich will nicht dass irgendwelche anderen Typen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E eu não quero que nenhum outro cara</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И я не хочу чтобы другие парни</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E non voglio che nessun altro ragazzo</span></p><p begin="1:30.770" end="1:33.350" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:30.770" end="1:30.950">Ta</span><span begin="1:30.950" end="1:31.120">king</span> <span begin="1:31.120" end="1:31.300">my</span> <span begin="1:31.300" end="1:31.500">pla</span><span begin="1:31.500" end="1:31.630">ce,</span> <span begin="1:31.630" end="1:31.800">girl,</span> <span begin="1:31.800" end="1:31.950">I</span> <span begin="1:31.990" end="1:32.150">got</span> <span begin="1:32.150" end="1:32.500">too</span> <span begin="1:32.500" end="1:32.750">mu</span><span begin="1:32.750" end="1:32.820">ch</span> <span begin="1:32.820" end="1:33.300">pri</span><span begin="1:33.300" end="1:33.350">de</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">来觊觎我的位置 女孩 我可是有点小骄傲的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">來覬覦我的位置 女孩 我可是有點小驕傲的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">僕の場所を奪われたくない プライドが高すぎるんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 자리를 빼앗는 건 싫어, 걸, 난 자존심이 너무 세거든</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Prenant ma place ma belle j&apos;ai trop de fierté</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tomando mi lugar, chica, tengo demasiado orgullo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Meinen Platz einnehmen Mädchen ich habe zu viel Stolz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tome o meu lugar, garota, eu tenho orgulho demais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Заняли моё место девочка у меня слишком много гордости</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Prenda il mio posto, ragazza, ho troppo orgoglio</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:31.800" end="1:33.350"><span begin="1:31.800" end="1:31.950">(I</span> <span begin="1:31.990" end="1:32.110">got</span> <span begin="1:32.150" end="1:32.440">too</span> <span begin="1:32.500" end="1:32.750">mu</span><span begin="1:32.750" end="1:32.820">ch</span> <span begin="1:32.820" end="1:33.300">pri</span><span begin="1:33.300" end="1:33.350">de)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我可是有点小骄傲的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我可是有點小驕傲的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">プライドが高すぎるんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">난 자존심이 너무 세거든</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J&apos;ai trop de fierté</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tengo demasiado orgullo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich habe zu viel Stolz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu tenho orgulho demais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">У меня слишком много гордости</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ho troppo orgoglio</span></span></p><p begin="1:33.520" end="1:37.530" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:33.520" end="1:33.710">I</span> <span begin="1:33.710" end="1:34.010">know</span> <span begin="1:34.010" end="1:34.210">I</span> <span begin="1:34.210" end="1:34.550">may</span> <span begin="1:34.550" end="1:34.880">be</span> <span begin="1:34.880" end="1:35.550">wrong,</span> <span begin="1:35.730" end="1:35.900">bu</span><span begin="1:35.900" end="1:35.940">t</span> <span begin="1:35.940" end="1:36.080">I</span> <span begin="1:36.080" end="1:36.290">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:36.290" end="1:36.430">wan</span><span begin="1:36.430" end="1:36.610">na</span> <span begin="1:36.610" end="1:36.780">be</span> <span begin="1:36.780" end="1:36.980">r</span><span begin="1:36.980" end="1:37.530">ight</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我知道我或许有些偏执 但我宁愿将错就错</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我知道我或許有些偏執 但我寧願將錯就錯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">間違っているかもしれない けど正しくなんてなりたくない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 틀렸을지도 모르지만, 옳은 사람이 되고 싶진 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je sais que j&apos;ai peut-être tort mais je ne veux pas avoir raison</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sé que podría estar equivocado, pero no quiero tener la razón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich weiß ich liege vielleicht falsch aber ich will gar nicht im Recht sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu sei que posso estar errado, mas não quero estar certo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я знаю что могу ошибаться но я не хочу быть правым</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">So che forse sbaglio, ma non voglio aver ragione</span></p><p begin="1:37.630" end="1:40.510" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:37.630" end="1:38.210">&apos;Cau</span><span begin="1:38.210" end="1:38.280">se</span> <span begin="1:38.280" end="1:38.840">your</span> <span begin="1:38.840" end="1:39.000">li</span><span begin="1:39.000" end="1:39.160">ps</span> <span begin="1:39.160" end="1:39.500">were</span> <span begin="1:39.500" end="1:39.810">made</span> <span begin="1:39.810" end="1:40.000">for</span> <span begin="1:40.000" end="1:40.510">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只因你的双唇天生就该被我亲吻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只因你的雙唇天生就該被我親吻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君の唇は僕のものになるために作られたから</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 입술은 내 입술을 위해 만들어졌으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Car tes lèvres ont été faites pour les miennes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque tus labios fueron hechos para los míos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Denn deine Lippen sind für meine gemacht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque os seus lábios foram feitos para os meus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведь твои губы созданы для моих</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché le tue labbra sono state fatte per le mie</span></p><p begin="1:40.860" end="1:43.200" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:40.860" end="1:41.040">And</span> <span begin="1:41.040" end="1:41.500">my</span> <span begin="1:41.500" end="1:41.710">heart</span> <span begin="1:41.870" end="1:41.940">would</span> <span begin="1:42.050" end="1:42.210">go</span> <span begin="1:42.310" end="1:42.410">f</span><span begin="1:42.410" end="1:42.740">lat</span><span begin="1:42.740" end="1:43.200">line</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我的心跳大概会骤然停息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我的心跳大概會驟然停息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そして僕の心臓は止まってしまうだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그리고 내 심장은 멈춰버리고 말 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et mon cœur s&apos;arrêterait de battre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y mi corazón se detendría</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und mein Herz würde aufhören zu schlagen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E o meu coração iria parar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А моё сердце бы просто остановилось</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E il mio battito si azzererebbe</span></p><p begin="1:43.580" end="1:47.300" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:43.580" end="1:43.670">I</span><span begin="1:43.670" end="1:43.770">f</span> <span begin="1:43.770" end="1:44.090">i</span><span begin="1:44.090" end="1:44.250">t</span> <span begin="1:44.250" end="1:44.520">wa</span><span begin="1:44.520" end="1:44.610">s</span><span begin="1:44.610" end="1:44.940">n&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:44.940" end="1:45.270">bea</span><span begin="1:45.270" end="1:45.430">ting</span> <span begin="1:45.430" end="1:45.800">for</span> <span begin="1:45.800" end="1:46.130">you</span> <span begin="1:46.130" end="1:46.470">all</span> <span begin="1:46.470" end="1:46.520">the</span> <span begin="1:46.640" end="1:47.300">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">倘若它不是每时每刻都在为你跳动</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">倘若它不是每時每刻都在為你跳動</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">いつも君のために脈打っていなければ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">항상 널 위해 뛰고 있는 게 아니라면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S&apos;il ne battait pas pour toi tout le temps</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si no estuviera latiendo por ti todo el tiempo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn es nicht die ganze Zeit nur für dich schlagen würde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se não estivesse batendo por você o tempo todo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если бы оно не билось всё время ради тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se non battesse per te tutto il tempo</span></p><p begin="1:47.480" end="1:52.430" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.480" end="1:47.590">Uh,</span> <span begin="1:47.960" end="1:48.190">so</span> <span begin="1:48.190" end="1:48.290">i</span><span begin="1:48.290" end="1:48.370">f</span> <span begin="1:48.370" end="1:48.720">I</span> <span begin="1:48.720" end="1:49.080">get</span> <span begin="1:49.190" end="1:49.580">jea</span><span begin="1:49.580" end="1:49.710">lou</span><span begin="1:49.710" end="1:49.890">s,</span> <span begin="1:51.080" end="1:51.420">I</span> <span begin="1:51.420" end="1:51.870">can</span><span begin="1:51.870" end="1:51.940">&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:51.940" end="1:52.300">hel</span><span begin="1:52.300" end="1:52.340">p</span> <span begin="1:52.340" end="1:52.430">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">嗯 所以若我吃醋嫉妒 那也是情难自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">嗯 所以若我吃醋嫉妒 那也是情難自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ああ 嫉妬しても 仕方がないんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어, 그러니 내가 질투하더라도, 어쩔 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah alors si je suis jaloux je n&apos;y peux rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ay, así que si me pongo celoso, no puedo evitarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah wenn ich also eifersüchtig werde kann ich nichts dafür</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">É, então se eu fico com ciúmes, não consigo evitar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ох поэтому если я ревную ничего не могу с собой поделать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" x