入凡間的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は天使に違いない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넌 틀림없이 천사일 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu dois être un ange</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Debes ser un ángel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du musst ein Engel sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você deve ser um anjo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты должно быть ангел</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Devi essere un angelo</span></p><p begin="2:21.920" end="2:23.220" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:21.920" end="2:22.040">Pu</span><span begin="2:22.040" end="2:22.120">t</span> <span begin="2:22.120" end="2:22.310">you</span> <span begin="2:22.310" end="2:22.450">in</span> <span begin="2:22.450" end="2:22.560">a</span> <span begin="2:22.560" end="2:22.630">f</span><span begin="2:22.630" end="2:22.970">rame,</span> <span begin="2:22.970" end="2:23.220">ooh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">真想把你珍藏进画框里 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">真想把你珍藏進畫框裡 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君を額縁に飾りたい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">널 액자에 담아두고 싶어, 우</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Te mettre dans un cadre ouh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Te pondría en un marco, oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich würde dich am liebsten einrahmen oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Te colocaria numa moldura, ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поместить бы тебя в рамку оох</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Da metterti in una cornice, oh</span></p><p begin="2:23.290" end="2:24.570" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.290" end="2:23.460">Ba</span><span begin="2:23.460" end="2:23.630">by,</span> <span begin="2:23.630" end="2:23.800">who</span> <span begin="2:23.800" end="2:23.970">could</span> <span begin="2:23.970" end="2:24.010">b</span><span begin="2:24.010" end="2:24.330">lame</span> <span begin="2:24.330" end="2:24.570">you?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">宝贝 谁又能舍得怪你呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">寶貝 誰又能捨得怪你呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ベイビー 誰が君を責められる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">베이비, 누가 널 탓하겠어?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Bébé qui pourrait t&apos;en blâmer ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nena, ¿quién podría culparte?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schatz wer könnte es dir verübeln</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Baby, quem poderia te culpar?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Малышка кто бы мог тебя винить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Piccola, chi potrebbe biasimarti?</span></p><p begin="2:24.640" end="2:26.320" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:24.640" end="2:24.820">Gla</span><span begin="2:24.820" end="2:24.860">d</span> <span begin="2:24.860" end="2:25.020">your</span> <span begin="2:25.020" end="2:25.190">ma</span><span begin="2:25.190" end="2:25.360">ma</span> <span begin="2:25.360" end="2:25.670">ma</span><span begin="2:25.670" end="2:25.710">de</span> <span begin="2:25.710" end="2:26.320">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">万分庆幸你母亲带你降临人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">萬分慶幸你母親帶你降臨人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君を産んでくれたママに感謝するよ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">널 낳아주신 네 어머니께 감사해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Heureux que ta maman t&apos;ait faite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Agradezco que tu mamá te haya dado la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bin froh dass deine Mama dich zur Welt gebracht hat</span><span ttm:r