ne peux pas être expliquée ouh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No tienes explicación, oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lässt dich nicht erklären oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não pode ser explicada, ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тебя невозможно описать оох</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non puoi essere spiegata, oh</span></p><p begin="2:30.070" end="2:32.080" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:30.070" end="2:30.270">You</span> <span begin="2:30.270" end="2:30.360">mu</span><span begin="2:30.360" end="2:30.480">st</span> <span begin="2:30.480" end="2:30.670">be</span> <span begin="2:30.670" end="2:30.800">an</span> <span begin="2:30.800" end="2:31.130">an</span><span begin="2:31.130" end="2:32.080">gel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你一定是不慎坠入凡间的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你一定是不慎墜入凡間的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は天使に違いない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넌 틀림없이 천사일 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu dois être un ange</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Debes ser un ángel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du musst ein Engel sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você deve ser um anjo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты должно быть ангел</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Devi essere un angelo</span></p><p begin="2:32.840" end="2:35.120" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:32.840" end="2:33.170">Ow</span><span begin="2:33.170" end="2:33.350">ne</span><span begin="2:33.350" end="2:33.410">r</span> <span begin="2:33.410" end="2:33.610">o</span><span begin="2:33.610" end="2:33.750">f</span> <span begin="2:33.750" end="2:34.190">my</span> <span begin="2:34.190" end="2:35.070">hear</span><span begin="2:35.070" end="2:35.120">t</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我心房的唯一主人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我心房的唯一主人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">僕の心の持ち主</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 심장의 주인</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Celle qui possède mon cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dueña de mi corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Herrin meines Herzens</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dona do meu coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хозяйка моего сердца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Padrona del mio cuore</span></p><p begin="2:35.560" end="2:37.880" itunes:key="L50" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:35.560" end="2:35.940">Tat</span><span begin="2:36.060" end="2:36.410">too</span><span begin="2:36.410" end="2:36.460">ed</span> <span begin="2:36.460" end="2:36.950">your</span> <span begin="2:36.950" end="2:37.860">mar</span><span begin="2:37.860" end="2:37.880">k</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将你的印记深深刻作刺青</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將你的印記深深刻作刺青</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君の印を刻み込んだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">네 흔적을 문신으로 새겼어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu as tatoué ta marque</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tatuaste tu marca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hast dein Zeichen tätowiert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tatuou a sua marca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Оставила свой след словно тату</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Hai tatuato il tuo marchio</span></p><p begin="2:38.300" end="2:42.350" itunes:key="L51" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:38.300" end="2:38.750">There</span> <span begin="2:38.750" end="2:39.180">for</span> <span begin="2:39.180" end="2:39.630">the</span> <span begin="2:39.630" end="2:40.170">whole</span> <span begin="2:40.170" end="2:40.430">world</span> <span begin="2:40.430" end="2:40.990">to</span> <span begin="2:40.990" end="2:42.350">see</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就那样向全世界高调宣示</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就那樣向全世界高調宣示</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">世界中に見えるように</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">온 세상이 다 볼 수 있도록</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Là pour que le monde entier la voie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ahí para que todo el mundo la vea</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass die ganze Welt es sehen kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Lá para o mundo inteiro ver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чтобы видел весь мир</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lì in modo che il mondo intero possa vederlo</span></p><p begin="2:42.900" end="2:46.020" itunes:key="L52" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:42.900" end="2:43.220">You&apos;re</span> <span begin="2:43.220" end="2:43.650">the</span> <span begin="2:43.750" end="2:44.070">ow</span><span begin="2:44.070" end="2:44.240">ne</span><span begin="2:44.240" end="2:44.290">r</span> <span begin="2:44.290" end="2:44.520">o</span><span begin="2:44.520" end="2:44.620">f</span> <span begin="2:44.620" end="2:45.090">my</span> <span begin="2:45.090" end="2:45.980">hear</span><span begin="2:45.980" end="2:46.020">t</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你是我心房的唯一主人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你是我心房的唯一主人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は僕の心の持ち主</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넌 내 심장의 주인이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu es celle qui possède mon cœur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Eres la dueña de mi corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du bist die Herrin meines Herzens</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você é a dona do meu coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты хозяйка моего сердца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sei la padrona del mio cuore</span></p><p begin="2:46.480" end="2:48.850" itunes:key="L53" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:46.480" end="2:46.860">An</span><span begin="2:46.980" end="2:47.010">d</span> <span begin="2:47.010" end="2:47.230">all</span> <span begin="2:47.350" end="2:47.650">my</span> <span begin="2:47.650" end="2:47.850">s</span><span begin="2:47.850" end="2:48.730">car</span><span begin="2:48.730" end="2:48.850">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">也抚平了我所有的伤痕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">也撫平了我所有的傷痕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">そして僕のすべての傷跡の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 모든 상처의 주인도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et toutes mes cicatrices</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y de todas mis cicatrices</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und all meiner Narben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E de todas as minhas cicatrizes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И всех моих шрамов</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E di tutte le mie cicatrici</span></p><p begin="2:49.200" end="2:53.310" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:49.200" end="2:49.540">Ba</span><span begin="2:49.540" end="2:49.770">by,</span> <span begin="2:49.770" end="2:50.060">you</span> <span begin="2:50.060" end="2:50.500">got</span> <span begin="2:50.500" end="2:50.860">su</span><span begin="2:50.860" end="2:50.910">ch</span> <span begin="2:50.910" end="2:51.050">a</span> <span begin="2:51.050" end="2:51.420">hol</span><span begin="2:51.420" end="2:51.460">d</span> <span begin="2:51.460" end="2:51.770">on</span> <span begin="2:51.900" end="2:52.870">me,</span> <span begin="2:52.870" end="2:53.310">so</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">宝贝 你就是这样让我彻底沦陷 所以</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">寶貝 你就是這樣讓我徹底淪陷 所以</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ベイビー 君は僕をすっかり夢中にさせているから</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">베이비, 넌 날 완전히 사로잡았어, 그러니</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Bébé tu as une telle emprise sur moi alors</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nena, tienes tanto control sobre mí, así que</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schatz du hast mich so sehr im Griff also</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Baby, você me tem tanto em suas mãos, então</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Малышка у тебя такая власть надо мной поэтому</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Piccola, hai una tale presa su di me, quindi</span></p><p begin="2:53.400" end="2:57.940" itunes:key="L55" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:53.400" end="2:53.650">So</span> <span begin="2:53.650" end="2:53.740">i</span><span begin="2:53.740" end="2:53.820">f</span> <span begin="2:53.820" end="2:54.170">I</span> <span begin="2:54.170" end="2:54.530">get</span> <span begin="2:54.640" end="2:55.040">jea</span><span begin="2:55.040" end="2:55.160">lou</span><span begin="2:55.160" end="2:55.350">s,</span> <span begin="2:56.540" end="2:56.860">I</span> <span begin="2:56.860" end="2:57.320">can</span><span begin="2:57.320" end="2:57.390">&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:57.390" end="2:57.750">hel</span><span begin="2:57.750" end="2:57.790">p</span> <span begin="2:57.790" end="2:57.940">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">所以若我吃醋嫉妒 那也是情难自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">所以若我吃醋嫉妒 那也是情難自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">だから嫉妬しても 仕方がないんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그러니 내가 질투하더라도, 어쩔 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors si je suis jaloux je n&apos;y peux rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Así que si me pongo celoso, no puedo evitarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn ich also eifersüchtig werde kann ich nichts dafür</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Então se eu fico com ciúmes, não consigo evitar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поэтому если я ревную ничего не могу с собой поделать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quindi se divento geloso, non ci posso fare niente</span></p><p begin="2:59.230" end="3:05.350" itunes:key="L56" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:59.230" end="2:59.620">I</span> <span begin="2:59.620" end="3:00.110">wan</span><span begin="3:00.110" end="3:00.150">t</span> <span begin="3:00.150" end="3:00.470">eve</span><span begin="3:00.470" end="3:00.630">ry</span> <span begin="3:00.630" end="3:00.940">bi</span><span begin="3:00.940" end="3:00.990">t</span> <span begin="3:00.990" end="3:01.130">of</span> <span begin="3:01.130" end="3:01.780">you,</span> <span begin="3:01.780" end="3:01.980">I</span> <span begin="3:01.980" end="3:02.160">gue</span><span begin="3:02.160" end="3:02.330">ss</span> <span begin="3:02.330" end="3:02.750">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="3:02.750" end="3:03.180">sel</span><span begin="3:03.180" end="3:03.390">fi</span><span begin="3:03.390" end="3:03.520">sh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我想要霸占你的每一分每一寸 我想我就是这般自私</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我想要霸佔你的每一分每一寸 我想我就是這般自私</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君の全てが欲しい 僕は自分勝手なんだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너의 모든 것을 원해, 내가 이기적인가 봐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux chaque parcelle de toi je suppose que je suis égoïste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero cada parte de ti, supongo que soy egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich will jedes Stückchen von dir ich glaube ich bin selbstsüchtig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu quero cada pedacinho seu, acho que sou egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу каждую частичку тебя наверное я эгоист</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio ogni singola parte di te, credo di essere egoista</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="3:03.350" end="3:05.350"><span begin="3:03.350" end="3:03.540">(Gue</span><span begin="3:03.540" end="3:03.710">ss</span> <span begin="3:03.710" end="3:04.050">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="3:04.160" end="3:04.460">sel</span><span begin="3:04.550" end="3:05.230">fi</span><span begin="3:05.230" end="3:05.350">sh)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我想我就是这般自私</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我想我就是這般自私</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">きっと僕は自分勝手なんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 이기적인가 봐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je suppose que je suis égoïste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Supongo que soy egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich glaube ich bin selbstsüchtig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Acho que sou egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Наверное я эгоист</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Credo di essere egoista</span></span></p><p begin="3:04.510" end="3:09.860" itunes:key="L57" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:04.510" end="3:04.580">I</span><span begin="3:04.580" end="3:04.700">t&apos;s</span> <span begin="3:04.700" end="3:05.030">bad</span> <span begin="3:05.030" end="3:05.370">for</span> <span begin="3:05.370" end="3:05.570">my</span> <span begin="3:05.570" end="3:05.880">men</span><span begin="3:05.880" end="3:06.160">tal,</span> <span begin="3:06.590" end="3:07.150">bu</span><span begin="3:07.150" end="3:07.210">t</span> <span begin="3:07.440" end="3:07.780">I</span> <span begin="3:07.780" end="3:08.250">can&apos;t</span> <span begin="3:08.250" end="