"3:14.090" end="3:14.140">de</span> <span begin="3:14.140" end="3:14.260">it,</span> <span begin="3:14.760" end="3:16.350">no</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你光芒万丈地出门 却又藏不住那份迷人 不</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你光芒萬丈地出門 卻又藏不住那份迷人 不</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君がそんな風に綺麗に着飾っても 隠しきれないよ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그렇게 눈부신 모습으로 외출할 때면, 숨길 수 없잖아, 아니</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu sors aussi radieuse et tu ne peux pas le cacher non</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sales luciendo como lo haces, pero no puedes ocultarlo, no</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du so wunderschön aussiehst und du kannst es nicht verbergen nein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você sai linda desse jeito, mas você não pode esconder isso, não</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты выходишь в свет такая ослепительная и этого не скрыть нет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Esci e sei così splendida, ma non puoi nasconderlo, no</span></p><p begin="3:16.470" end="3:17.750" itunes:key="L59" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:16.470" end="3:16.590">Pu</span><span begin="3:16.590" end="3:16.670">t</span> <span begin="3:16.670" end="3:16.860">you</span> <span begin="3:16.860" end="3:17.000">in</span> <span begin="3:17.000" end="3:17.110">a</span> <span begin="3:17.110" end="3:17.180">f</span><span begin="3:17.180" end="3:17.520">rame,</span> <span begin="3:17.520" end="3:17.750">ooh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">真想把你珍藏进画框里 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">真想把你珍藏進畫框裡 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君を額縁に飾りたい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">널 액자에 담아두고 싶어, 우</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Te mettre dans un cadre ouh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Te pondría en un marco, oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich würde dich am liebsten einrahmen oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Te colocaria numa moldura, ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поместить бы тебя в рамку оох</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Da metterti in una cornice, oh</span></p><p begin="3:17.830" end="3:19.110" itunes:key="L60" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:17.830" end="3:18.000">Ba</span><span begin="3:18.000" end="3:18.190">by,</span> <span begin="3:18.190" end="3:18.340">who</span> <span begin="3:18.340" end="3:18.410">could</span> <span begin="3:18.510" end="3:18.550">b</span><span begin="3:18.550" end="3:18.880">lame</span> <span begin="3:18.880" end="3:19.110">you?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">宝贝 谁又能舍得怪你呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">寶貝 誰又能捨得怪你呢？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ベイビー 誰が君を責められる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">베이비, 누가 널 탓하겠어?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Bébé qui pourrait t&apos;en blâmer ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nena, ¿quién podría culparte?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schatz wer könnte es dir verübeln</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Baby, quem poderia te culpar?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Малышка кто бы мог тебя винить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Piccola, chi potrebbe biasimarti?</span></p><p begin="3:19.190" end="3:22.460" itunes:key="L61" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:19.190" end="3:19.370">Gla</span><span begin="3:19.370" end="3:19.410">d</span> <span begin="3:19.410" end="3:19.570">your</span> <span begin="3:19.570" end="3:19.710">ma</span><span begin="3:19.710" end="3:19.910">ma</span> <span begin="3:19.910" end="3:20.220">ma</span><span begin="3:20.220" end="3:20.260">de</span> <span begin="3:20.260" end="3:20.840">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">万分庆幸你母亲带你降临人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">萬分慶幸你母親帶你降臨人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君を産んでくれたママに感謝するよ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">널 낳아주신 네 어머니께 감사해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Heureux que ta maman t&apos;ait faite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Agradezco que tu mamá te haya dado la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bin froh dass deine Mama dich zur Welt gebracht hat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que bom que a sua mãe te fez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я так рад что твоя мама родила тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sono grato che tua madre ti abbia messa al mondo</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="3:20.550" end="3:22.460"><span begin="3:20.550" end="3:20.730">(Gla</span><span begin="3:20.730" end="3:20.770">d</span> <span begin="3:20.770" end="3:20.880">your</span> <span begin="3:20.910" end="3:21.060">ma</span><span begin="3:21.100" end="3:21.250">ma</span> <span begin="3:21.290" end="3:21.580">ma</span><span begin="3:21.580" end="3:21.620">de</span> <span begin="3:21.620" end="3:22.460">you)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">万分庆幸你母亲带你降临人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">萬分慶幸你母親帶你降臨人世</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君を産んでくれたママに感謝するよ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">널 낳아주신 네 어머니께 감사해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Heureux que ta maman t&apos;ait faite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Agradezco que tu mamá te haya dado la vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bin froh dass deine Mama dich zur Welt gebracht hat</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que bom que a sua mãe te fez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я так рад что твоя мама родила тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:l