ml:lang="ko">날 미치게 만들어, 넌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu me rends fou</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me vuelves loco, tú</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du treibst mich in den Wahnsinn du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me deixando louco, você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты сводишь меня с ума</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi fai impazzire, tu</span></p><p begin="3:34.180" end="3:35.480" itunes:key="L69" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:34.180" end="3:34.360">Can</span><span begin="3:34.360" end="3:34.540">not</span> <span begin="3:34.540" end="3:34.680">be</span> <span begin="3:34.680" end="3:34.890">ex</span><span begin="3:34.890" end="3:35.120">plained,</span> <span begin="3:35.230" end="3:35.480">ooh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">美得根本无法用言语描摹 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">美得根本無法用言語描摹 喔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">説明なんてできない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">설명할 수가 없어, 우</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu ne peux pas être expliquée ouh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No tienes explicación, oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lässt dich nicht erklären oh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não pode ser explicada, ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тебя невозможно описать оох</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non puoi essere spiegata, oh</span></p><p begin="3:35.530" end="3:37.540" itunes:key="L70" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:35.530" end="3:35.730">You</span> <span begin="3:35.730" end="3:35.820">mu</span><span begin="3:35.820" end="3:35.940">st</span> <span begin="3:35.940" end="3:36.130">be</span> <span begin="3:36.130" end="3:36.260">an</span> <span begin="3:36.260" end="3:36.590">an</span><span begin="3:36.590" end="3:37.540">gel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你一定是不慎坠入凡间的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你一定是不慎墜入凡間的天使</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君は天使に違いない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넌 틀림없이 천사일 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu dois être un ange</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Debes ser un ángel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du musst ein Engel sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você deve ser um anjo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты должно быть ангел</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Devi essere un angelo</span></p><p begin="3:38.290" end="3:41.630" itunes:key="L71" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:38.290" end="3:38.680">Jea</span><span begin="3:38.680" end="3:38.850">lou</span><span begin="3:38.850" end="3:38.990">s,</span> <span begin="3:40.010" end="3:40.200">bu</span><span begin="3:40.200" end="3:40.240">t</span> <span begin="3:40.240" end="3:40.390">I</span> <span begin="3:40.510" end="3:41.000">can&apos;t</span> <span begin="3:41.000" end="3:41.420">hel</span><span begin="3:41.420" end="3:41.460">p</span> <span begin="3:41.460" end="3:41.630">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为你吃醋嫉妒 但我也情难自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為你吃醋嫉妒 但我也情難自禁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">嫉妬してしまうけど 仕方がないんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">질투 나지만, 어쩔 수 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Jaloux mais je n&apos;y peux rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Celoso, pero no puedo evitarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eifersüchtig aber ich kann nichts dafür</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com ciúmes, mas não consigo evitar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ревную но ничего не могу с собой поделать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Geloso, ma non ci posso fare niente</span></p><p begin="3:42.890" end="3:47.150" itunes:key="L72" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:42.890" end="3:43.230">I</span> <span begin="3:43.230" end="3:43.750">wan</span><span begin="3:43.750" end="3:43.790">t</span> <span begin="3:43.790" end="3:44.050">e</span><span begin="3:44.050" end="3:44.100">ve</span><span begin="3:44.100" end="3:44.160">ry</span> <span begin="3:44.260" end="3:44.580">bi</span><span begin="3:44.580" end="3:44.620">t</span> <span begin="3:44.620" end="3:44.790">of</span> <span begin="3:44.790" end="3:45.420">you,</span> <span begin="3:45.420" end="3:45.510">I</span> <span begin="3:45.630" end="3:45.800">gue</span><span begin="3:45.800" end="3:45.990">ss</span> <span begin="3:45.990" end="3:46.390">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="3:46.390" end="3:46.790">sel</span><span begin="3:46.790" end="3:46.990">fi</span><span begin="3:46.990" end="3:47.150">sh</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我想要霸占你的每一分每一寸 我想我就是这般自私</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我想要霸佔你的每一分每一寸 我想我就是這般自私</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君の全てが欲しい 僕は自分勝手なんだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너의 모든 것을 원해, 내가 이기적인가 봐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux chaque parcelle de toi je suppose que je suis égoïste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quiero cada parte de ti, supongo que soy egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich will jedes Stückchen von dir ich glaube ich bin selbstsüchtig</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu quero cada pedacinho seu, acho que sou egoísta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я хочу каждую частичку тебя наверное я эгоист</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio ogni singola parte di te, credo di essere egoista</span></p></div></body></tt>